{"tid":1375107,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇聽過四面楚歌？不如下次勇武同警犬對峙既時候 對住警犬講英文","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:05:03.000Z","uid":49246,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61df49db73d23f885ecc3a45f4420c79994b0d20","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"利申尊重同支搏現場前線任何決定 <br />\n極度要推呢個post <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373325\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373325</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚睇live 見到前線對峙係咁用廣東話屌防暴老母 侮辱佢地係香港之恥 <br />\n呢類說話只會令個班冇思想冇分析能力既警犬好嬲加發癲<br />\n<br />\n純屬自己ff 警犬洗腦工程肯定同佢地講愈比人屌 代表佢地愈岩<br />\n<br />\n好想做到分化佢地 擾亂軍心 <br />\n尋日不亂諗一個成語<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四面楚歌</span></strong></span><br />\n要用聲音呢種力量 直接擾亂對家軍心 令對家未開拖 已經淆底<br />\n<br />\n用英文屌前排班冇思想 冇分析能力既毅進仔 會唔會令到佢地淆底 怯呢？<br />\n再仆街啲 分埋次序<br />\n 搵一個前線用英文屌完 另一個前線問警犬：聽唔明呀？我用中文譯返比你地啦毅進仔<br />\n<br />\n（利申：自己英文差 日常生活遇到英文都會先自己怯一怯 我相信毅進仔同樣）<br />\n<br />\n純ff 唔係話超撚有用 但試下無紡<br />\n就算唔係用英文 大家諗下有咩可以做到 輕鬆擾亂對方軍心 搞撚到警犬淆底 會唔會出現前排警犬掉低gear投降？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四面楚歌</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcf6fd13b2d63e2429bc3a327fcf06f51e920b2d","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"這時項羽軍隊的軍糧快要吃盡了，又被漢軍團團包圍，情勢十分危急。但是劉邦也有點兒畏懼這位蓋世英雄，因此暫時「按兵不動」。這時張良又獻計，建議劉邦改用心理戰，於是他調集了大批漢軍，練唱楚國歌曲。在一個漆黑、寂靜的夜裡，張良忽然吹起簫來，並且命令圍在楚軍營帳外的漢軍們，開始唱起悲戚的楚歌。歌聲淒淒，迴盪在軍營裡，使得楚國的士兵們不禁勾起了思鄉的情緒，一時間個個都傷心落淚。<br />\n　　項羽聽到楚歌，也低聲飲泣；看到隨自己征戰無數的子弟兵，一個個「黯然神傷」的樣子，不禁也失去了「決一死戰」的決心。這時，項羽最心愛的虞姬，知道「大勢已去」，便拔劍自殺了。項羽看到這番情景，想到自己再也無臉回去見「江東父老」了，於是就握著一柄寶劍，騎上烏騅馬，衝出重圍，在烏江邊上「舉劍自刎」而死。「四面楚歌」強調一個人四面受敵孤立無援，到了無路可走的境地。"},{"pid":"b9cd5fb107f82d74a749653721bd3c385a9f9c99","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1601aa9a0dde330484c93d531b0e9328048db56d","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cb1aeba3436a6914b8043039d0ea54742c7b8ef","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b20c3ea6b16af867a1b9079e96a82a12aaa704d8","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"若巴打覺得我9up冇用<br />\n屌我等我唔好再推 由佢沉"},{"pid":"1689a9306c18de3f7357c26c2971f0d6b0ca3ae8","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0674ec33a166a13e6c6ff53f2a372da71e80f517","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2fc65ca47ed7e9b4010201760eaa6a34a88eb86","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff89243576d72cfd3004a49c9ffa5f6a290763a0","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d56a90087953263f848828a1edc89b4a6fde5f52","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"2a9684234bc47d2a757271b3eb1dafad3362cdd9","tid":1375107,"uid":260296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"新穎<br />\n<br />\n利伸試過用黎對付廢中老 有奇效"},{"pid":"ba04de7c716b9269842e62189fe7f77610528b42","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a9684234bc47d2a757271b3eb1dafad3362cdd9","tid":1375107,"uid":260296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:35:13.000Z","msg":"新穎<br />\n<br />\n利伸試過用黎對付廢中老 有奇效"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:35:55.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦！！！"},{"pid":"705eec3bacebd3ee4c91cbf3dca1e4bded8259e6","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"兩邊推"},{"pid":"1b40b49d1b20d3722c485275d4c9288e79bfb094","tid":1375107,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2b5da614270e819f8a1e4249bff25c6c92925c","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f9390403ddd56f806ddbe4a4c91a91e3ff91e5d","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8865ebdcc9663e477a2a0be27c7b26a420b4bbb7","tid":1375107,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp3%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=67a67885\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"3d0c791498cc4dd1ca9567156b45f0822d94da3a","tid":1375107,"uid":265113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b08fe04e385a573b5eee69e610aedef9192ff83","tid":1375107,"uid":49246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56fcfd2711bd05cada3f07bfcd6b47128e610c